uest systems in place?\n\nFor example, [GitHub Issues](https://docs.github.com/en/issues/tracking-your-work-with-issues/about-issues) can be used to report bugs or request features, as it provides a clear, trackable way to manage contributions. GitHub's customizable issue templates and forms can be configured to pre-fill fields like titles, labels, and assignees, and even include form-style inputs. [Read more](https://docs.github.com/en/communities/using-templates-to-encourage-useful-issues-and-pull-requests/configuring-issue-templates-for-your-repository) to learn about configuring issue templates. "},"title":{"changed":false},"uuid":"1ccaaff5-e6c3-4c88-83db-40fc5c7fa1e9"},{"createdAt":"2025-07-14T10:50:22.003Z","entityUuid":"6f205c29-4fd3-4a3e-9e67-adb032c1c58c","eventType":"MoveQuestionEvent","parentUuid":"991fac78-95fb-4486-a96f-f396e5f67e55","targetUuid":"3063ce18-7a96-40fd-9d0b-fb12d4d78f3d","uuid":"4557129a-04a1-4994-b2cc-f5c3d36bab4c"},{"annotations":[],"createdAt":"2025-07-14T10:51:26.203Z","entityUuid":"4fab61c1-e79e-4241-a7e8-9fb17fcc165e","eventType":"AddQuestionEvent","parentUuid":"3507700c-768c-48c2-9242-eb1338191711","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","requiredPhaseUuid":null,"tagUuids":[],"text":null,"title":"","uuid":"e9aa7bed-c9e7-457f-bb06-b20c478c4a57"},{"annotations":{"changed":false},"answerUuids":{"changed":false},"createdAt":"2025-07-14T10:51:26.243Z","entityUuid":"4fab61c1-e79e-4241-a7e8-9fb17fcc165e","eventType":"EditQuestionEvent","expertUuids":{"changed":false},"parentUuid":"3507700c-768c-48c2-9242-eb1338191711","questionType":"OptionsQuestion","referenceUuids":{"changed":false},"requiredPhaseUuid":{"changed":false},"tagUuids":{"changed":false},"text":{"changed":true,"value":"Do/will you include tests for your software?"},"title":{"changed":true,"value":"Testing"},"uuid":"2b36c401-69ea-412d-958b-65a05efb766a"},{"annotations":{"changed":false},"createdAt":"2025-07-14T10:51:31.132Z","entityUuid":"3507700c-768c-48c2-9242-eb1338191711","eventTy